name: RUN BEETLE RUN
description:
Not even anyone could resist being thrown into a foreign world. Where those moments are always struggling through pleasure in changes that are getting dirtier, smellier and give you life at the same time. With all the timed awareness, the biggest question is whether we are still questioning that throw that is getting narrower, weaker and stronger?

----------------------------------------------

"RUN BEETLE RUN"

Bahkan siapapun tidak mampu menolak keterlemparannya dalam sebuah dunianya yang asing.  Di mana momen-momen itu selalu bergumul melalui kenikmatan dalam perubahan-perubahan yang semakin kotor, bau sekaligus memberimu kehidupan. Dengan segala kesadaran yang mewaktu, pertanyaan terbesar ialah masihkah kita mempertanyakan keterlemparan itu yang semakin menyempit, melemah dan menguat?

5000x5000px 300dpi - Digital artwork
100% hand drawn 
Full blessed - chkws
